Name: SNOMEDCTBodyStructures
Title: SNOMED CT Body Structures
Descriptino: This value set includes all codes from [SNOMED CT](http://snomed.info/sct) where concept is-a 442083009 (Anatomical or acquired body site (body structure)).

Name: ObservationReferenceRangeAppliesToCodes
Title: Observation Reference Range Applies To Codes
Descriptino: This value set defines a set of codes that can be used to indicate the particular target population the reference range applies to.

Name: ObservationReferenceRangeMeaningCodes
Title: Observation Reference Range Meaning Codes
Descriptino: This value set defines a set of codes that can be used to indicate the meaning/use of a reference range for a particular target population.

Name: PHVS_JobSupervisoryLevelorPayGrade_ODH
Title: Job Supervisory Level or Pay Grade (ODH)
Descriptino: An indicator of responsibilities of a person's job for directing work and personnel management, as reported by the person. Pay grade is used to represent supervisory or personnel management responsibilities for U.S. military service, because it conveys similar meaning across branches of service.

Name: WorkClassificationODH
Title: WorkClassificationODH
Descriptino: Provide the concepts for the value element of the C-CDA Work Classification Observation entry template.

Name: WorkScheduleODH
Title: WorkScheduleODH
Descriptino: Describes an individual's typical arrangement of working hours for an occupation.

Name: EmploymentStatusODH
Title: employmentStatusODH
Descriptino: Concepts representing whether a person does or does not currently have a job or is not currently in the labor pool seeking employment.

Name: YesNoVS
Title: Yes No VS
Descriptino: Value set indicating yes or no (values drawn from Snomed CT), equivalent to LL361-7.
